{"tid":2439218,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"傳理想汽車、蔚來汽車及小鵬汽車最快今年在港上市","createTime":"2021-03-09T05:49:28.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-09T08:22:25.000Z","uid":50386,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"491844acbb22d1bc7262bd718d6c4269735ad6a4","tid":2439218,"uid":50386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T05:49:28.000Z","msg":"《路透》引述消息人士報道，於美國上市的理想汽車(<a href=\"http://LI.US\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FLI.US&d=eGp%2FCvHI00KNC8mlo1Mhy6HDOfwBZUVptSzBKRgi4hA%3D&h=4a9c9e47\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">LI.US</a>)、蔚來汽車(<a href=\"http://NIO.US\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FNIO.US&d=eGp%2FCvHI00KNC8mlo1Mhy6HDOfwBZUVptSzBKRgi4hA%3D&h=b833374e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">NIO.US</a>)及小鵬汽車(<a href=\"http://XPEV.US\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FXPEV.US&d=eGp%2FCvHI00KNC8mlo1Mhy6HDOfwBZUVptSzBKRgi4hA%3D&h=5380bc90\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">XPEV.US</a>)計劃最快今年在香港上市，3間公司有意將擴大後股本至少有5%作上市，以周一收市價計算，集資額約為50億美元。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，3間車廠一直在與顧問合作，研究最早可能在年中尋求上市，以滿足亞洲投資者的需求<br />\n<br />\n根據港交所(<a href=\"http://00388.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F00388.HK&d=eGp%2FCvHI00KNC8mlo1Mhy6HDOfwBZUVptSzBKRgi4hA%3D&h=586dbace\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">00388.HK</a>)規定，尋求第二上市的公司必須在另一個交易所上市期間至少有兩個財年有良好的合規監管。據悉，由於理想汽車及小鵬汽車於去年中才在美國上市，故很有可能會在香港申請雙重上市。同時有消息人士稱，小鵬汽車還考慮在上海科創板進行第三度上市。"},{"pid":"b001ca343695e152f988bc6759f51fc46eee3521","tid":2439218,"uid":253752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T05:50:37.000Z","msg":"3傻跌到pk <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c9d7dcacb6b2d1c801543abd0c1626d49b9869e","tid":2439218,"uid":249162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T05:53:07.000Z","msg":"弱智，你估哩到真係咁大個池？個鳩個黎都可以做